<h2><span>著作信息</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p>别看了，这里面什么都没有的。</p>
<p><span style="color: transparent">都说了没有，还看，嗯？（微笑）</span></p>
<p>链世挽歌版式修改自<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sekai-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4476849); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4476849&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610088832" alt="Sekai_s" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4476849)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sekai-s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4476849); return false;">Sekai_s</a></span>创作的linkAge版式，感谢！<br />
懒人作者页代码来自<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/w-asriel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3317001); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3317001&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610088832" alt="W Asriel" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3317001)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/w-asriel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3317001); return false;">W Asriel</a></span>，感谢！</p>
