<p>便当便当醋溜便当飞机场Phate我可以！！！顺便贴贴TE☆</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6062512&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610088832" alt="YUANNN" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6062512)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;">YUANNN</a></span></p>
</div>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>写作心得：<strong>把自己当成一只鸽子，永远不要以为自己能写出一个续集。</strong>每当你写完一个故事/SCP，看看它能否独立于将来的部分。就如<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(571081); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=571081&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610088832" alt="qntm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=571081)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(571081); return false;">qntm</a></span>所述，在关键的地方吊胃口写个“未完待续”并不能起到预想中的效果。</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610088832" alt="TimeElapsed" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;">TimeElapsed</a></span></p>
</div>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
